msgstr "Klarte ikkje å logga inn i domenet"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:12
msgid "Enterprise Login"
msgstr "Verksemdsinnlogging"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:13
msgid ""
"Enterprise login allows an existing centrally managed user account to be "
"used on this device. You can also use this account to access company "
"resources on the internet."
msgstr ""
"Verksemdsinnlogging tillèt at ein eksisterande sentralt handsama brukarkonto "
"kan verte brukt på denne eininga. Du kan òg bruka denne kontoen for å nå "
"verksemdsressursar på nettet."

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:27
#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:153
msgid "_Domain"
msgstr "_Domene"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:40
#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-local.ui:104
msgid "_Username"
msgstr "_Brukarnamn"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:53
#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/password/gis-password-page.ui:31
msgid "_Password"
msgstr "_Passord"

# Eg finn ikkje eit godt ord for «realm».
#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:99
msgid "Enterprise domain or realm name"
msgstr "Verksemdsdomene eller -namn"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:126
msgid "Domain Administrator Login"
msgstr "Innlogging for domeneadminstrator"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:141
msgid ""
"In order to use enterprise logins, this computer needs to be enrolled in a "
"domain. Please have your network administrator type the domain password "
"here, and choose a unique computer name for your computer."
msgstr ""
"For å kunne bruke verksemdsinnloggingar lyt denne datamaskina vera meldt inn "
"i eit domene. Få nettverksadministratoren din til å skriva domenepassordet "
"her, og vel eit unikt datamaskinnamn for maskina di."

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:179
msgid "_Computer"
msgstr "D_atamaskin"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:203
msgid "Administrator _Name"
msgstr "Administrator_namn"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:227
msgid "Administrator Password"
msgstr "Administratorpassord"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-enterprise.ui:260
msgid "C_ontinue"
msgstr "_Hald fram"

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-local.c:321
msgid "We need a few details to complete setup."
msgstr "Vi treng nokre få detaljar for å fullføra oppsettet."

#: gnome-initial-setup/pages/account/gis-account-page-local.c:476
